    <section class="hero">
      <div class="wrap">
        <span class="eyebrow">Wellington</span>
        <h1>Cleaning jobs in Wellington.</h1>
        <p class="lead">Apply once to be considered for Spruce-standard cleaning work across Wellington and the greater region. We review every application individually and contact suitable applicants about a next step.</p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/apply/">Apply now <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></a>
          <a class="btn btn-outline" href="/how-it-works/">How it works</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block tint">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="reliable-split">
          <div class="reliable-left">
            <span class="eyebrow">Across the region</span>
            <h2>Cleaning work across Wellington.</h2>
            <p class="callout">Wellington leans heavily toward commercial and office work.</p>
            <p>As the capital, Wellington has a compact, hilly centre packed with government and corporate offices, which drives steady demand for scheduled commercial cleans. Residential work is spread across the surrounding suburbs and the greater region, so where you can be considered depends on the areas you can reach and the hours you can cover.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tick-panel">
            <div class="tick-list">
              <div class="tick-row"><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12l4 4 10-10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span class="lbl">Wellington central, Te Aro and Thorndon</span></div>
              <div class="tick-row"><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12l4 4 10-10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span class="lbl">Western suburbs (Kelburn, Karori)</span></div>
              <div class="tick-row"><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12l4 4 10-10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span class="lbl">Eastern and southern suburbs (Miramar, Kilbirnie, Newtown)</span></div>
              <div class="tick-row"><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12l4 4 10-10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span class="lbl">Northern suburbs (Johnsonville, Tawa)</span></div>
              <div class="tick-row"><span class="check" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12l4 4 10-10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span><span class="lbl">Greater Wellington (Lower Hutt, Upper Hutt, Porirua)</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="sec-head">
          <span class="eyebrow">Work types</span>
          <h2>The cleaning work you could be allocated in Wellington</h2>
          <p>The capital's mix tilts toward offices and commercial sites, with residential work across the hills and valleys. Suitable Spruce-certified cleaners are considered for three broad areas.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="types-groups">
          <div class="tgroup">
            <span class="label">Homes</span>
            <h3>Residential cleaning</h3>
            <p class="blurb">Regular and one-off cleans across Wellington's suburbs and the Hutt Valley, plus end-of-tenancy work in a tight rental market.</p>
            <ul><li>Residential cleaning</li><li>Deep cleaning</li><li>End of tenancy</li></ul>
          </div>
          <div class="tgroup">
            <span class="label">Business</span>
            <h3>Office &amp; commercial</h3>
            <p class="blurb">Strong demand from government and corporate offices in the CBD, plus retail and commercial sites across the region.</p>
            <ul><li>Office cleaning</li><li>Commercial cleaning</li></ul>
          </div>
          <div class="tgroup">
            <span class="label">Specialist</span>
            <h3>Trades-adjacent &amp; add-on</h3>
            <p class="blurb">Builders' and handover cleans, carpet and upholstery support, and window cleaning support.</p>
            <ul><li>Builders &amp; handover cleans</li><li>Carpet &amp; upholstery support</li><li>Window cleaning support</li></ul>
