            <span class="eyebrow">Why apply here</span>
            <h2>One application for cleaning work across the capital.</h2>
            <p>Wellington's centre is small but its work is spread from the waterfront offices to the Hutt and Porirua. Apply once and we keep your details on file, then consider suitable applicants as demand comes up.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="why-panel">
            <div class="why-rows">
              <div class="why-row"><span class="n">01</span><div><h3>One place to apply</h3><p>Apply once for Wellington cleaning work instead of role by role.</p></div></div>
              <div class="why-row"><span class="n">02</span><div><h3>Built for commercial</h3><p>Onboarding and training to the Spruce standard, which suits the capital's heavy office and commercial demand.</p></div></div>
              <div class="why-row"><span class="n">03</span><div><h3>Matched to your area</h3><p>Considered for work based on your location, transport, availability, and certification.</p></div></div>
