          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/apply/">Start application <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></a>
