    <section class="block faq-block">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="sec-head">
          <span class="eyebrow">Wellington questions</span>
          <h2>Applying in Wellington</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you cover the Hutt Valley and Porirua?<span class="ico" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span></summary><div class="answer"><p>Yes. Demand spans greater Wellington, so cleaners based in Lower Hutt, Upper Hutt, and Porirua are often well placed for work near them. Apply with your location and we'll know which areas you can cover.</p></div></details>
          <details class="faq-item"><summary>Is there more office work than home work here?<span class="ico" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span></summary><div class="answer"><p>Often, yes. As the capital, Wellington has heavy office and commercial demand, alongside residential work across the suburbs. We ask which work types you suit in the application.</p></div></details>
          <details class="faq-item"><summary>Do the hills and transport matter?<span class="ico" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span></summary><div class="answer"><p>They can. Wellington is compact but hilly, and public transport is good in the centre. We ask about your location and transport so we can match you to realistic work.</p></div></details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
